{"body": "I think looking forward XML will no longer be relevant for the rails core. As @pixeltrix mentioned already the parser has been moved outside of Rails and this is a clear transition away from XML.\r\n\r\nBesides that we need to have very good reasons to add more methods to core classes. I think this is something that you can do in a gem or your application but should not go into Rails.\r\n\r\nI'm :-1: on this one.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/14948494", "created_at": "2013-03-15T08:35:09Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/9721#issuecomment-14948494", "updated_at": "2013-03-15T08:35:09Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 9721, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/senny", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/3d698e2872c07061a455d9e250861235?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fd1359f9934ee5a75ed441ffce412a0a1.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/received_events", "gravatar_id": "3d698e2872c07061a455d9e250861235", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "senny", "type": "User", "id": 5402, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237e73ebd3543c151009536"}, "id": 14948494, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/9721"}
